FBIS3-18168 "drweu039_p_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 GREECE Officials Comment on Role of EU's Van Den Broek NC2502223494 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1800 GMT 25 Feb 94 NC2502223494 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] Answering correspondent's questions, Deputy Foreign Minister Yeoryios Papandreou and government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos today referred to European Union [EU] Commissioner Hans Van Den Broek's mediation role. [Begin recording] [Papandreou] Van Den Broek was given orders by the EU Council of Ministers and the European Commission to play the initial mediation role. And this is the role he is playing. [Venizelos] In his capacity as EU Commissioner, Mr. Van Den Broek is interested in the respect of political law, something that concerns the European Commission in almost all cases. [end recording]
